    ns1:hasDescription "In summary, the Goods comprise: the provision of one (1) Static Bespoke Immersive Simulation Exercise Unit Suite (including both Hardware and Software Technologies) and two (2) Mobile Units (including Hardware and Software Technologies) along with the relevant software licences, and, software and hardware maintenance contracts, for the Garda College."@eng ;
