<http://data.europa.eu/a4g/resource/id_dd4ca65c-1d8b-412c-a4f2-150c5b2852ea-01_SubmissionTermProcedure_49f47df6b2a16ef8d72cef0e8ca41317> a ns1:ProcedureSpecificTerm,
